# MERN Stack Project

This is a full-stack web application built using the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React, and Node.js). It provides a modern, responsive, and scalable architecture for developing web applications.

## Features

- User authentication (Sign up, Login, Logout).
- CRUD operations for data management.
- Responsive and visually appealing UI/UX.
- API integration with backend services.
- Real-time updates using WebSockets (if applicable).
- Deployed on [platform name, e.g., Heroku, Vercel].

## Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: React, Tailwind CSS (or your preferred CSS framework)
- **Backend**: Node.js, Express.js
- **Database**: MongoDB (with Mongoose ORM)
